# Museum Display
This script displays animations on powerstones.

## Requirements
- 1 script and 14 lines in the Facility AI
- Turbo scripts ([Turbo V2](https://github.com/Xenos6666/TPT2_scripts/tree/main/common/turbo_exec) is recommended for frame syncing, but the [execution stack](https://github.com/Xenos6666/TPT2_scripts/tree/main/common/execution_stack) can be used instead)

## How to use

Impulse Key - 3

Set `framerepeat`, `frametotal`, and `framesize` to the number of times a frame repeats, the number of frames in the animation string, and the number of characters in each string respectively

Paste one of these strings on top of "Paste string here" at line 10 or make your own using https://github.com/TheZoraiz/ascii-image-converter/blob/master/README.md

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FtutLA63Cp8
